message.content: cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.SY. The paper discusses the development of intelligent autonomous agents for cyber defense, which involves the use of artificial intelligence and machine learning techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG) to detect and react to hostile activities in a network (cs.CR). The paper also touches on the planning and collaboration aspects of these agents (cs.SE, cs.SY).
